    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> E, F, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You focus Chakra through your sound amplifier, firing a powerful blast of sound that deals 4d6 sonic damage (Fortitude halves) and deafening creatures in the area for 1d4 rounds (Fortitude negates).</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to increase the damage by 1d6, up to 1d6 per 2 levels or 10d6.</p>\n\n",
